query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  COUNT(riskLevel) as has_risk_level,
  COUNT(governancePath) as has_governance_path,
  COUNT(missionAlignmentRating) as has_mission_rating,
  COUNT(missionAlignmentReasoning) as has_mission_reasoning,
  COUNT(riskReasoning) as has_risk_reasoning
FROM initiatives;
